<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4597149>
    dc:description "FIG. 7.— Gazella sp.(A-D, G, H) and Oioceros atropatenes Rodler & Weithofer,1890 (E, F) from Ivand locality (NW Iran):A, B, HMNH-IV140 in frontal (A) and lateral (B) views; C, D, HMNH-IV138 in frontal (C) and lateral (D) views; E, F, HMNH-IV200 in lateral-posterior (E) and frontal (F) views; G, H, HMNH-IV139 in lateral (G) and frontal (H) views. Scale bars: A, B, G, H, 20 mm; C, D, 15 mm; E, F, 25 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4597149/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

